# Installation

## 1. Create Namespace

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/00-namespace.yaml
```

---

## 2. Install Coroot Operator

```bash
helm repo add coroot https://coroot.github.io/helm-charts
helm repo update

helm install coroot-operator coroot/coroot-operator -n coroot
```

---

## 3. Create Coroot Instance

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/01-coroot-cr.yaml
```

---

## 4. Disable Operator Node-Agent

```bash
oc patch ds coroot-node-agent \
  -n coroot \
  --type=merge \
  --patch-file coroot/02-disable-operator-node-agent-patch.yaml
```

---

## 5. Deploy Custom Node-Agent

```bash
oc adm policy add-scc-to-user privileged \
  -z coroot-node-agent-custom \
  -n coroot

oc apply -f coroot/03-node-agent-custom.yaml
```

---

## 6. Expose Coroot UI

```bash
oc apply -f coroot/04-coroot-route.yaml
```

---

## 7. Get Route

```bash
oc get route coroot -n coroot
```

---

