# Deploy Demo Applications

## Simple Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f apps/traffic-demo/00-traffic-demo.yaml
oc apply -f apps/traffic-demo/01-traffic-generator.yaml
```

---

## Advanced Traffic Demo

```bash
oc apply -f apps/traffic-demo/02-traffic-demo-advanced.yaml
oc apply -f apps/traffic-demo/03-traffic-generator-advanced.yaml
```

---

## Online Boutique Demo

```bash
oc apply -f apps/boutique/00-namespace.yaml

oc apply -n boutique -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo/main/release/kubernetes-manifests.yaml

bash apps/boutique/01-anyuid-scc.sh

oc rollout restart deploy -n boutique

oc apply -f apps/boutique/02-frontend-route.yaml
```

---

## Spring Boot Coroot Demo

Deploy namespace:

```bash
oc apply -f apps/k8s/namespace.yaml
```

Deploy application:

```bash
oc apply -f apps/k8s/deployment.yaml
oc apply -f apps/k8s/service.yaml
oc apply -f apps/k8s/ingress.yaml
```

Verify:

```bash
oc get pods -n java-demo
oc get svc -n java-demo
oc get ingress -n java-demo
```

Generate traffic:

```bash
while true; do
  curl http://java-coroot-demo.java-demo.svc.cluster.local:8080/random
  curl http://java-coroot-demo.java-demo.svc.cluster.local:8080/slow
  curl http://java-coroot-demo.java-demo.svc.cluster.local:8080/error
  sleep 1
done
```

Coroot will automatically discover:

* Services
* HTTP traffic
* Errors
* Latency
* CPU usage
* Memory usage
* Service dependencies

---

# Validation

## Check Node Agent Health

```bash
oc logs -n coroot \
  -l app.kubernetes.io/component=coroot-node-agent-custom \
  --tail=30
```

Expected:

```text
metrics remote write endpoint: http://coroot-coroot.coroot:8080/v1/metrics
sent metrics in XXms
```

---

## Verify Coroot Components

```bash
oc get pods -n coroot
oc get svc -n coroot
oc get route -n coroot
```

Expected:

```text
coroot-coroot
coroot-clickhouse
coroot-cluster-agent
coroot-node-agent-custom
coroot-prometheus
```

