# Functional Capability Matrix

| Capability                 | Status     | Notes                         |
| -------------------------- | ---------- | ----------------------------- |
| Infrastructure Metrics     | ✅ Enabled  | Full node/container metrics   |
| Service Map / Topology     | ✅ Enabled  | Auto-discovery works          |
| Network Traffic Visibility | ✅ Enabled  | TCP/basic HTTP visibility     |
| Continuous Profiling       | ✅ Enabled  | CPU profiling active          |
| Root Cause Analysis        | ✅ Partial  | Based on infra + metrics      |
| HTTP Deep Tracing          | ❌ Disabled | No payload/L7 deep inspection |
| TLS Payload Visibility     | ❌ Disabled | No decrypted TLS traces       |
| Advanced App Tracing       | ❌ Disabled | Requires full L7 tracing      |

